== 計畫終止 ==
2019年10月10日，[[Nike|Nike]]宣布將終止奧勒岡計畫<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nike shuts down Oregon Project after ban of coach|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-athletics-nike/nike-shuts-down-oregon-project-after-ban-of-coach-idUSKBN1WQ0GT|last=Corner|first=Jahmal|date=2019-10-11|language=en-US|access-date=2020-12-31|work=Reuters|archive-date=2020-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225061047/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-athletics-nike/nike-shuts-down-oregon-project-after-ban-of-coach-idUSKBN1WQ0GT|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/10/sports/nike-oregon-project-salazar.html|title=Nike to Shut Down Salazar’s Oregon Project|last=Futterman|first=Matthew|date=2019-10-11|website=The New York Times|language=en-US|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2019-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225182219/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/10/sports/nike-oregon-project-salazar.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，執行長{{Link-en|馬克·帕克|Mark Parker}}表示，計畫總教練{{Link-en|艾柏特·薩拉札|Alberto Salazar}}強迫選手瘦身，要求使用停經藥和[[利尿劑|利尿劑]]的行為，甚至對其言語羞辱<ref>{{Cite web|title=田徑》美國女跑者訓練遭虐待想輕生 教練對「變態行徑」做出解釋|url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2976469|author=吳孟儒|date=2019-11-13|language=zh-TW|access-date=2020-12-30|work=自由電子報|archive-date=2020-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222045034/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2976469|dead-url=no}}</ref>，造成了他們無法專心在訓練以及達成比賽目標；目前仍在計畫中的選手將協助安排其他訓練計畫<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nike closing Oregon Project in wake of Salazar doping ban|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/nike-closing-oregon-project-wake-salazar-ban-66204381|last=Harris|first=Rob|date=2019-10-12|language=en-US|access-date=2020-12-31|work=abc NEWS|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813154342/https://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/nike-closing-oregon-project-wake-salazar-ban-66204381|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

